<h1>Stan Stewart</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://muz4now.com/now/">muz4now.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Ithaca
NY
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Composer, performer, improviser
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
See that? I'm going to turn it into music. (I like to call it spontaneous composition, though it's usually known as improvisation.)
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I create music because it is like the escape valve for my soul.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
I'm a recovering serious person.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
Music In Our Lives by Jonathan L Friedmann.  Most of my favorite books have not been published yet. (Not kidding. I have several author friends.)
</p>

